# Mechanical Portfolio — Devendra Singh

Welcome — this repo highlights my mechanical design work, skills, and certifications.

About
I am a mechanical design engineer focused on CAD-driven product design, FEA validation, and manufacturing support. This portfolio includes representative projects, engineering notebooks, CAD models and verification reports.

Quick links
