- Résumé: resume.pdf

Selected Projects
1. High-efficiency axial fan — CAD, FEA, and manufacturing drawings (projects/high-efficiency-axial-fan)
2. Compact gearbox design — bearings selection & detailed stress analysis (projects/compact-gearbox)
3. Welded frame optimization — topology study and reduced mass (projects/welded-frame-optimization)

How this repo is organized
- /projects — Each project has its own folder with README, images and CAD exports
- /assets — photos, headshots, logos
- resume.pdf — latest résumé
- LICENSE — license for shared text or code

